                <h1>CDL Background Check: Ensuring Safe Drivers</h1>
                <p>A CDL background check is a crucial process for ensuring that individuals applying for a Commercial Driver's License meet safety and qualification standards. It involves reviewing driving records, criminal history, and employment verification. This check helps maintain road safety by identifying potential risks associated with candidates.</p>
